## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3855f-315">同时<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>对字符的缓冲区进行编码, 而不是按字符对字符进行编码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-315">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> encodes a buffer of characters all at once, rather than character by character.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3855f-316">如果遇到任何编码错误, <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Flush%2A>则调用方法时将引发异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-316">An exception is thrown when the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Flush%2A> method is called if any encoding errors are encountered.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3855f-317">属性仅适用<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>于用指定的<xref:System.IO.Stream>或用指定的文件名创建的实例。 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-317">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property only applies to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances that are created either with the specified <xref:System.IO.Stream> or with the specified file name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3855f-318">如果使用指定<xref:System.IO.TextWriter>的创建<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>实例, 则会通过基础的编码重写属性。 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-318">If the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance is created with the specified <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property is overridden by the encoding of the underlying <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3855f-319">例如, 如果将此属性设置为特定<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>的 Unicode (utf-16), 但基础写入器<xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>是 (派生自<xref:System.IO.TextWriter>), 其编码设置为 UTF8, 则输出将为 utf-8 编码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-319">For example, if this property is set to Unicode (UTF-16) for a particular <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>, but the underlying writer is a <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> (which derives from <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>) with its encoding set to UTF8, the output will be UTF-8 encoded.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3855f-320">如果该<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>实例是用其他 output 参数创建的, <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A>则忽略该属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-320">If the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance is created with other output parameters, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property is ignored.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3855f-321">如下示例中：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-321">In the following example:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3855f-322"><xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> 的默认值为 `Encoding.UTF8`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-322">The default value of <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> is `Encoding.UTF8`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3855f-323">设置为`Encoding.Unicode` , 并且<xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>的<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A>编码<xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>会重写该设置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-323">The <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> is set to `Encoding.Unicode` and the <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>'s encoding overrides the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> setting.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3855f-324">输出将为`Encoding.Unicode`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-324">The output will be `Encoding.Unicode`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using (StreamWriter output =  
    new StreamWriter(new FileStream("Xml01.xml", FileMode.Create), Encoding.Unicode))  
{  
    using (XmlWriter xmlWriter =  
        XmlWriter.Create(output, new XmlWriterSettings()))  
    {  
        xmlWriter.WriteStartDocument();  
        xmlWriter.WriteStartElement("Root");  
        xmlWriter.WriteEndElement();  
        xmlWriter.WriteEndDocument();  
    }  
}  
```  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="3855f-325">不要接受<xref:System.Text.Encoding>来自不受信任源的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3855f-325">Do not accept an <xref:System.Text.Encoding> object from an untrusted source.</span></span>  
  
   
  
